                    <description>&lt;p&gt;see &lt;a href=&quot;http://search.lucidimagination.com/search/document/f5f2af7c5041a79e/default_core&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://search.lucidimagination.com/search/document/f5f2af7c5041a79e/default_core&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
